01:54:23.000 --> 01:54:25.999
while you're already moving up?

01:54:26.000 --> 01:54:26.999
That's basically telling me to die.

01:54:27.000 --> 01:54:31.999
They don't arrive at the same time.

01:54:32.000 --> 01:54:33.999
They made this seriously difficult.

01:54:34.000 --> 01:54:36.999
You have to react immediately.

01:54:37.000 --> 01:54:38.999
Wait, then shoot when this one comes.

01:54:39.000 --> 01:54:40.999
Jump down. Okay.

01:54:41.000 --> 01:54:42.999
Down, down, down—then come right back up.

01:54:43.000 --> 01:54:43.999
Come straight up. Come

01:54:44.000 --> 01:54:44.999
Come up now! Down again!

01:54:45.000 --> 01:54:45.999
Come down again.

01:54:46.000 --> 01:54:46.999
Go now! Come here!

01:54:47.000 --> 01:54:50.999
Come down—why?

01:54:51.000 --> 01:54:51.999
I wasn't jumping; I was trying to go down.

01:54:52.000 --> 01:54:55.999
Try it. I'll do it here.

01:54:56.000 --> 01:54:57.999
This character doesn't suit me.

01:54:58.000 --> 01:54:59.999
Playing your main is best.

01:55:00.000 --> 01:55:01.999
Hyung, I'm finished now.

01:55:02.000 --> 01:55:02.999
Hey, I'm still alive!

01:55:03.000 --> 01:55:03.999
Okay, I killed it!

01:55:04.000 --> 01:55:05.999
Oh!

01:55:06.000 --> 01:55:07.999
It ended the second I arrived!

01:55:08.000 --> 01:55:10.999
That was too easy.

01:55:11.000 --> 01:55:12.999
You have to collect all of these, hyung.

01:55:13.000 --> 01:55:13.999
All of them.

01:55:14.000 --> 01:55:16.999
What? Yoo-hoo! Oh, I'm dead.

01:55:17.000 --> 01:55:24.999
[Laughs]

01:55:25.000 --> 01:55:26.999
Great. With that,

01:55:27.000 --> 01:55:27.999
we've defeated the boss

01:55:28.000 --> 01:55:28.999
and can wrap up today's game.

01:55:29.000 --> 01:55:30.999
That's all of part two.

01:55:31.000 --> 01:55:31.999
This is when Mom tells you to come home.

01:55:32.000 --> 01:55:33.999
You have to head back

01:55:34.000 --> 01:55:34.999
because dinner is waiting at home.

01:55:35.000 --> 01:55:35.999
It's starting to get dark.

01:55:36.000 --> 01:55:37.999
Stay out this late and Mom really scolds you.

01:55:38.000 --> 01:55:39.999
Right. And if we play too long,

01:55:40.000 --> 01:55:40.999
the hyungs behind us scold us too.

01:55:41.000 --> 01:55:42.999
They're waiting right behind us.

01:55:43.000 --> 01:55:45.999
Standing back there while they scold us.

01:55:46.000 --> 01:55:47.999
All right.

01:55:48.000 --> 01:55:48.999
My whole body is soaked.

01:55:49.000 --> 01:55:49.999
Seriously.

01:55:50.000 --> 01:55:52.999
You could wring the sweat out of me.

01:55:53.000 --> 01:55:54.999
So, after today's dancing

01:55:55.000 --> 01:55:55.999
and the game,

01:55:56.000 --> 01:55:56.999
how was it overall?

01:55:57.000 --> 01:55:57.999
how was it?

01:55:58.000 --> 01:56:02.999
How was it?

01:56:03.000 --> 01:56:03.999
He says it was good.

01:56:04.000 --> 01:56:04.999
He says it was good.

01:56:05.000 --> 01:56:06.999
Stop copying everything I say.

01:56:07.000 --> 01:56:07.999
Me?

01:56:08.000 --> 01:56:08.999
I don't do that.

01:56:09.000 --> 01:56:09.999
You keep doing it.

01:56:10.000 --> 01:56:12.999
No, I don't.

01:56:13.000 --> 01:56:13.999
[Laughs]

01:56:14.000 --> 01:56:15.999
Let's do screenshot time.

01:56:16.000 --> 01:56:20.999
Screenshot time!

01:56:21.000 --> 01:56:26.999
, please pay your respects.

01:56:27.000 --> 01:56:28.999
One,

01:56:29.000 --> 01:56:29.999
two,

01:56:30.000 --> 01:56:32.999
three,

01:56:33.000 --> 01:56:34.999
four,

01:56:35.000 --> 01:56:38.999
five.

01:56:39.000 --> 01:56:42.999
Nice!
